{"tid":2204546,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梵蒂岡據報冀在中國設立常設代表處","createTime":"2020-09-16T06:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T04:20:30.000Z","uid":51665,"like":1,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"d70b941a493b9b4b545e125e994ef248b966d343","tid":2204546,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:34:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549892-20200916.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549892-20200916.htm&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvVlQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=a12a6d67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549892-20200916.htm&h=fe17ec5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549892-20200916.htm</a><br />\n天主教權威刊物《美國》期刊透露，梵蒂岡希望在中國設立常設代表處，以促成梵蒂岡國務卿帕羅林與總理李克強會面。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，中梵沒有外交關係，教廷一直希望在中國開設常設代表處，作為與中國政府及當地教會溝通的窗口，類似教廷在越南的做法，但被中國政府拒絕，北京的前提是教廷必須與台灣斷交。<br />\n<br />\n報道又說，為期兩年的中梵主教任命臨時協議下月到期，教廷已準備好延長協議，認為中梵協議具有作用，可藉此打開與中國直接對話的大門，包括解決主教任命爭議，促成中國教會生活正常化，以及在適當時機，觸及中梵自1951年中斷的外交關係問題。"},{"pid":"c344b43e2059f14c37c3ed7e4bf09320f4cbabbb","tid":2204546,"uid":51665,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"有冇耶撚可以解釋吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb1f0f00f184c3ae0b1b287037b94bb2ccd5db2","tid":2204546,"uid":44209,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"c344b43e2059f14c37c3ed7e4bf09320f4cbabbb","tid":2204546,"uid":51665,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"有冇耶撚可以解釋吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dMXAPOP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdMXAPOP.jpg&h=fac616ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e1e6a2f02bf6867772fcb6